            { id: '3', title: 'Your Legal Rights', description: 'Laws that protect you.', imageUrl: 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1589829085413-56de8ae18c73?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=600', content: `In East Africa, many countries have specific laws protecting survivors. In Kenya, the Sexual Offences Act and Protection Against Domestic Violence Act provide frameworks for justice. You have the right to a P3 form and free medical assessment at public hospitals.` }
